(***********************************************************************

 The bicategory of monads and lax morphisms

 We define the bicategory of monads and lax morphisms.

 Note: this is a different bicategory from the one defined in Monads.v.
 The bicategory defined in that file has 1-cells that preserve the unit
 and multiplication up to invertible 2-cell. The formal theory of monads
 as described by Street, makes use of the bicategory defined in this
 file.

 Contents
 1. The bicategory
 2. The univalence
 3. Projections and constructions
 4. Invertible 2-cells
 5. Equivalences of monads
 6. Underlying pseudofunctor

 ***********************************************************************)

Œ∑f: linvunitor (pr1 f) ‚Ä¢ (Œ∑x ‚ñπ pr1 f) =
(rinvunitor (pr1 f) ‚Ä¢ (pr1 f ‚óÉ Œ∑y)) ‚Ä¢ pr2 f
Œ∑g: linvunitor (pr1 g) ‚Ä¢ (Œ∑y ‚ñπ pr1 g) =
(rinvunitor (pr1 g) ‚Ä¢ (pr1 g ‚óÉ Œ∑z)) ‚Ä¢ pr2 g
((rinvunitor (pr1 f) ‚Ä¢ (pr1 f ‚óÉ Œ∑y)) ‚Ä¢ pr2 f) ‚ñπ pr1 g =
((((rinvunitor (pr1 f ¬∑ pr1 g) ‚Ä¢ (pr1 f ¬∑ pr1 g ‚óÉ Œ∑z))
   ‚Ä¢ rassociator (pr1 f) (pr1 g) (pr2 mz))
  ‚Ä¢ (pr1 f ‚óÉ pr2 g))
 ‚Ä¢ lassociator (pr1 f) (pr2 my) (pr1 g))
‚Ä¢ (pr2 f ‚ñπ pr1 g)

(pr1 f ‚óÉ pr2 g) ‚Ä¢ lassociator (pr1 f) (pr2 my) (pr1 g) =
?t2

        apply idpath.
      
B: bicat

   ‚Ä¢ ((pr1 f ‚óÉ pr2 g)
      ‚Ä¢ lassociator (pr1 f) (pr2 my) (pr1 g))) =

‚àè x y : end_bicat B,

 exact (Œª mx, pr2 mx ¬∑ pr2 mx ==> pr2 mx).
    
B: bicat
‚àè x y : end_bicat B,
(Œª mx : end_bicat B, pr2 mx ¬∑ pr2 mx ==> pr2 mx) x
‚Üí (Œª mx : end_bicat B, pr2 mx ¬∑ pr2 mx ==> pr2 mx) y
  ‚Üí end_bicat B ‚ü¶ x, y ‚üß ‚Üí UU
 exact (Œª mx my Œºx Œºy f,
             lassociator _ _ _
             ‚Ä¢ (pr2 f ‚ñπ _)
             ‚Ä¢ rassociator _ _ _
             ‚Ä¢ (_ ‚óÉ pr2 f)
             ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _
             ‚Ä¢ (Œºx ‚ñπ _)
             =
             (_ ‚óÉ Œºy)
             ‚Ä¢ pr2 f).
  Defined.

  Definition mnd_data
    : bicat
    := total_bicat disp_mnd_data.

  Definition is_mnd
             (m : mnd_data)
    : UU
    := let X := pr1 m in
       let f := pr12 m in
       let Œ∑ := pr122 m in
       let Œº := pr222 m in
       (linvunitor f ‚Ä¢ (Œ∑ ‚ñπ f) ‚Ä¢ Œº = id2 f)
       √ó
       (rinvunitor f ‚Ä¢ (f ‚óÉ Œ∑) ‚Ä¢ Œº = id2 f)
       √ó
       (rassociator _ _ _ ‚Ä¢ (f ‚óÉ Œº) ‚Ä¢ Œº
        =
        (Œº ‚ñπ f) ‚Ä¢ Œº).

    repeat (apply isapropdirprod) ; apply cellset_property.
  Qed.

(**
 3. Projections and constructions
 *)
Section MonadProjections.
  Context {B : bicat}
          (m : mnd B).

  Definition ob_of_mnd
    : B
    := pr1 m.

  Definition endo_of_mnd
    : ob_of_mnd --> ob_of_mnd
    := pr112 m.

  Definition unit_of_mnd
    : id‚ÇÅ _ ==> endo_of_mnd
    := pr1 (pr212 m).

  Definition mult_of_mnd
    : endo_of_mnd ¬∑ endo_of_mnd ==> endo_of_mnd
    := pr2 (pr212 m).

  Definition mnd_unit_left
    : linvunitor _ ‚Ä¢ (unit_of_mnd ‚ñπ _) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd = id2 _
    := pr122 m.

  Definition mnd_unit_right
    : rinvunitor _ ‚Ä¢ (_ ‚óÉ unit_of_mnd) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd = id2 _
    := pr1 (pr222 m).

  Definition mnd_mult_assoc
    : rassociator _ _ _ ‚Ä¢ (_ ‚óÉ mult_of_mnd) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd
      =
      (mult_of_mnd ‚ñπ _) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd
    := pr2 (pr222 m).

  
B: bicat
m: mnd B
(endo_of_mnd ‚óÉ mult_of_mnd) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd =
(lassociator endo_of_mnd endo_of_mnd endo_of_mnd
 ‚Ä¢ (mult_of_mnd ‚ñπ endo_of_mnd)) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd

  
B: bicat
m: mnd B
(endo_of_mnd ‚óÉ mult_of_mnd) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd =
(lassociator endo_of_mnd endo_of_mnd endo_of_mnd
 ‚Ä¢ (mult_of_mnd ‚ñπ endo_of_mnd)) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd

    
B: bicat
m: mnd B
(endo_of_mnd ‚óÉ mult_of_mnd) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd =
lassociator endo_of_mnd endo_of_mnd endo_of_mnd
‚Ä¢ ((mult_of_mnd ‚ñπ endo_of_mnd) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd)

    
B: bicat
m: mnd B
(is_invertible_2cell_lassociator endo_of_mnd
   endo_of_mnd endo_of_mnd) ^-1
‚Ä¢ ((endo_of_mnd ‚óÉ mult_of_mnd) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd) =
(mult_of_mnd ‚ñπ endo_of_mnd) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd

    
B: bicat
m: mnd B
rassociator endo_of_mnd endo_of_mnd endo_of_mnd
‚Ä¢ ((endo_of_mnd ‚óÉ mult_of_mnd) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd) =
(mult_of_mnd ‚ñπ endo_of_mnd) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd

    
B: bicat
m: mnd B
(rassociator endo_of_mnd endo_of_mnd endo_of_mnd
 ‚Ä¢ (endo_of_mnd ‚óÉ mult_of_mnd)) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd =
(mult_of_mnd ‚ñπ endo_of_mnd) ‚Ä¢ mult_of_mnd

    exact mnd_mult_assoc.
  Qed.
End MonadProjections.

Definition make_mnd_data
           {B : bicat}
           (x : B)
           (f : x --> x)
           (Œ∑ : id‚ÇÅ _ ==> f)
           (Œº : f ¬∑ f ==> f)
  : mnd_data B
  := x ,, (f ,, (Œ∑ ,, Œº)).

Definition make_mnd
           {B : bicat}
           (m : mnd_data B)
           (Hm : is_mnd B m)
  : mnd B
  := pr1 m ,, (pr2 m ,, Hm).

Section MonadMapProjections.
  Context {B : bicat}
          {m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ : mnd B}
          (f : m‚ÇÅ --> m‚ÇÇ).

  Definition mor_of_mnd_mor
    : ob_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ --> ob_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ
    := pr1 f.

  Definition mnd_mor_endo
    : mor_of_mnd_mor ¬∑ endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ ==> endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ ¬∑ mor_of_mnd_mor
    := pr112 f.

  Definition mnd_mor_unit
    : linvunitor _ ‚Ä¢ (unit_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ ‚ñπ _)
      =
      rinvunitor _ ‚Ä¢ (_ ‚óÉ unit_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ) ‚Ä¢ mnd_mor_endo
    := pr1 (pr212 f).

  Definition mnd_mor_mu
    : lassociator _ _ _
      ‚Ä¢ (mnd_mor_endo ‚ñπ _)
      ‚Ä¢ rassociator _ _ _
      ‚Ä¢ (_ ‚óÉ mnd_mor_endo)
      ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _
      ‚Ä¢ (mult_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ ‚ñπ _)
      =
      (_ ‚óÉ mult_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ)
      ‚Ä¢ mnd_mor_endo
    := pr2 (pr212 f).
End MonadMapProjections.

Definition mnd_mor_data
           {B : bicat}
           (m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ : mnd B)
  : UU
  := ‚àë (f : ob_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ --> ob_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ),
     f ¬∑ endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ
     ==>
     endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ ¬∑ f.

Definition make_mnd_mor_data
           {B : bicat}
           {m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ : mnd B}
           (f : ob_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ --> ob_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ)
           (f_e : f ¬∑ endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ
                  ==>
                  endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ ¬∑ f)
  : mnd_mor_data m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ
  := f ,, f_e.

Definition mnd_mor_laws
           {B : bicat}
           {m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ : mnd B}
           (f : mnd_mor_data m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ)
  : UU
  := (linvunitor _ ‚Ä¢ (unit_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ ‚ñπ _)
      =
      rinvunitor _ ‚Ä¢ (_ ‚óÉ unit_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ) ‚Ä¢ (pr2 f))
     √ó
     (lassociator _ _ _
      ‚Ä¢ (pr2 f ‚ñπ _)
      ‚Ä¢ rassociator _ _ _
      ‚Ä¢ (_ ‚óÉ pr2 f)
      ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _
      ‚Ä¢ (mult_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ ‚ñπ _)
      =
      (_ ‚óÉ mult_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ)
      ‚Ä¢ pr2 f).

Definition make_mnd_mor_laws
           {B : bicat}
           {m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ : mnd B}
           (f : mnd_mor_data m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ)
           (fŒ∑ : linvunitor _ ‚Ä¢ (unit_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ ‚ñπ _)
                 =
                 rinvunitor _ ‚Ä¢ (_ ‚óÉ unit_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ) ‚Ä¢ pr2 f)
           (fŒº : lassociator _ _ _
                 ‚Ä¢ (pr2 f ‚ñπ _)
                 ‚Ä¢ rassociator _ _ _
                 ‚Ä¢ (_ ‚óÉ pr2 f)
                 ‚Ä¢ lassociator _ _ _
                 ‚Ä¢ (mult_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ ‚ñπ _)
                 =
                 (_ ‚óÉ mult_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ)
                 ‚Ä¢ pr2 f)
  : mnd_mor_laws f
  := fŒ∑ ,, fŒº.

Definition make_mnd_mor
           {B : bicat}
           {m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ : mnd B}
           (f : mnd_mor_data m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ)
           (Hf : mnd_mor_laws f)
  : m‚ÇÅ --> m‚ÇÇ
  := pr1 f ,, (pr2 f ,, Hf) ,, tt.

Section MonadCellProjections.
  Context {B : bicat}
          {m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ : mnd B}
          {f‚ÇÅ f‚ÇÇ : m‚ÇÅ --> m‚ÇÇ}
          (œÑ : f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ).

  Definition cell_of_mnd_cell
    : mor_of_mnd_mor f‚ÇÅ ==> mor_of_mnd_mor f‚ÇÇ
    := pr1 œÑ.

  Definition mnd_cell_endo
    : mnd_mor_endo f‚ÇÅ ‚Ä¢ (_ ‚óÉ cell_of_mnd_cell)
      =
      (cell_of_mnd_cell ‚ñπ _) ‚Ä¢ mnd_mor_endo f‚ÇÇ
    := pr112 œÑ.
End MonadCellProjections.

Definition mnd_cell_data
           {B : bicat}
           {m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ : mnd B}
           (f‚ÇÅ f‚ÇÇ : m‚ÇÅ --> m‚ÇÇ)
  : UU
  := mor_of_mnd_mor f‚ÇÅ ==> mor_of_mnd_mor f‚ÇÇ.

Definition is_mnd_cell
           {B : bicat}
           {m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ : mnd B}
           {f‚ÇÅ f‚ÇÇ : m‚ÇÅ --> m‚ÇÇ}
           (œÑ : mnd_cell_data f‚ÇÅ f‚ÇÇ)
  : UU
  := mnd_mor_endo f‚ÇÅ ‚Ä¢ (_ ‚óÉ œÑ)
     =
     (œÑ ‚ñπ _) ‚Ä¢ mnd_mor_endo f‚ÇÇ.

Definition make_mnd_cell
           {B : bicat}
           {m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ : mnd B}
           {f‚ÇÅ f‚ÇÇ : m‚ÇÅ --> m‚ÇÇ}
           (œÑ : mnd_cell_data f‚ÇÅ f‚ÇÇ)
           (œÑ_e : is_mnd_cell œÑ)
  : f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
  := œÑ ,, ((œÑ_e ,, (tt ,, tt)) ,, tt).

œÑ‚ÇÅ = œÑ‚ÇÇ

  (Œª x : pr1 f‚ÇÅ ==> pr1 f‚ÇÇ, pr2 f‚ÇÅ ==>[ x] pr2 f‚ÇÇ)

p: cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ‚ÇÅ = cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ‚ÇÇ
pr1 œÑ‚ÇÅ = pr1 œÑ‚ÇÇ

œÑ‚ÇÅ, œÑ‚ÇÇ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
p: cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ‚ÇÅ = cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ‚ÇÇ
isPredicate
  (Œª x : pr1 f‚ÇÅ ==> pr1 f‚ÇÇ, pr2 f‚ÇÅ ==>[ x] pr2 f‚ÇÇ)

    
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B
f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
œÑ‚ÇÅ, œÑ‚ÇÇ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ

(**
 4. Invertible 2-cells
 *)
Section IsInvertibleMndCell.
  Context {B : bicat}
          {m‚ÇÅ m‚ÇÇ : mnd B}
          {f‚ÇÅ f‚ÇÇ : m‚ÇÅ --> m‚ÇÇ}
          {œÑ : f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ}
          (HœÑ : is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)).

  
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B
f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
œÑ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
HœÑ: is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)
f‚ÇÇ ==> f‚ÇÅ

  
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B
f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
œÑ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
HœÑ: is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)
f‚ÇÇ ==> f‚ÇÅ

    
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B
f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
œÑ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
HœÑ: is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)
mnd_cell_data f‚ÇÇ f‚ÇÅ
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B
f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
œÑ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
HœÑ: is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)
is_mnd_cell ?œÑ

    
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B
f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
œÑ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
HœÑ: is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)
mnd_cell_data f‚ÇÇ f‚ÇÅ
 exact (HœÑ^-1).
    
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B
f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
œÑ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
HœÑ: is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)
is_mnd_cell (HœÑ ^-1)
 abstract
        (cbn ;
         use vcomp_move_L_pM ; [ is_iso | ] ; cbn ;
         rewrite !vassocr ;
         use vcomp_move_R_Mp ; [ is_iso | ] ; cbn ;
         refine (!_) ;
         exact (mnd_cell_endo œÑ)).
  Defined.

  
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B
f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
œÑ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
HœÑ: is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)
is_invertible_2cell œÑ

  
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B
f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
œÑ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
HœÑ: is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)
is_invertible_2cell œÑ

    
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B
f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
œÑ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
HœÑ: is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)
f‚ÇÇ ==> f‚ÇÅ
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B

œÑ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
HœÑ: is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)
œÑ ‚Ä¢ ?œÜ = id‚ÇÇ f‚ÇÅ
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B
f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
œÑ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
HœÑ: is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)
?œÜ ‚Ä¢ œÑ = id‚ÇÇ f‚ÇÇ

    
B: bicat

f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
œÑ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ
HœÑ: is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)
f‚ÇÇ ==> f‚ÇÅ
 exact is_invertible_mnd_2cell_inverse.
    
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B
f‚ÇÅ, f‚ÇÇ: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
œÑ: f‚ÇÅ ==> f‚ÇÇ

œÑ ‚Ä¢ is_invertible_mnd_2cell_inverse = id‚ÇÇ f‚ÇÅ
 abstract
        (use eq_mnd_cell ; cbn ;
         apply vcomp_rinv).
    
B: bicat
m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ: mnd B

HœÑ: is_invertible_2cell (cell_of_mnd_cell œÑ)
is_invertible_mnd_2cell_inverse ‚Ä¢ œÑ = id‚ÇÇ f‚ÇÇ
 abstract
        (use eq_mnd_cell ; cbn ;
         apply vcomp_linv).
  Defined.
End IsInvertibleMndCell.

 exact (pr1 (HœÑ^-1)).

Defined.

(**
 5. Equivalences of monads
 *)
Section ToEquivalence.
  Context {B : bicat}
          {x : B}
          {mx mx' : disp_mnd B x}
          (m‚ÇÅ := x,, mx : mnd B)
          (m‚ÇÇ := x,, mx' : mnd B)
          (Hl : mx -->[ id‚ÇÅ x ] mx').

  Let l : m‚ÇÅ --> m‚ÇÇ := id‚ÇÅ x ,, Hl.

  Context (HŒ≥ : is_invertible_2cell (mnd_mor_endo l)).

  
B: bicat
x: B
mx, mx': disp_mnd B x
m‚ÇÅ:= x,, mx: mnd B
m‚ÇÇ:= x,, mx': mnd B
Hl: mx -->[ id‚ÇÅ x] mx'
l:= id‚ÇÅ x,, Hl: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
HŒ≥: is_invertible_2cell (mnd_mor_endo l)
mnd_mor_data m‚ÇÇ m‚ÇÅ

  
B: bicat
x: B
mx, mx': disp_mnd B x
m‚ÇÅ:= x,, mx: mnd B
m‚ÇÇ:= x,, mx': mnd B
Hl: mx -->[ id‚ÇÅ x] mx'
l:= id‚ÇÅ x,, Hl: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
HŒ≥: is_invertible_2cell (mnd_mor_endo l)
mnd_mor_data m‚ÇÇ m‚ÇÅ

    
B: bicat
x: B
mx, mx': disp_mnd B x

Hl: mx -->[ id‚ÇÅ x] mx'
l:= id‚ÇÅ x,, Hl: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
HŒ≥: is_invertible_2cell (mnd_mor_endo l)
B ‚ü¶ ob_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ, ob_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ ‚üß
B: bicat
x: B
mx, mx': disp_mnd B x
m‚ÇÅ:= x,, mx: mnd B

Hl: mx -->[ id‚ÇÅ x] mx'
l:= id‚ÇÅ x,, Hl: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß
HŒ≥: is_invertible_2cell (mnd_mor_endo l)
?f ¬∑ endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ ==> endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ ¬∑ ?f

 exact (id‚ÇÅ x).
    
B: bicat

mx, mx': disp_mnd B x

id‚ÇÅ x ¬∑ endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ ==> endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ ¬∑ id‚ÇÅ x
 exact (lunitor _
             ‚Ä¢ rinvunitor _
             ‚Ä¢ HŒ≥^-1
             ‚Ä¢ lunitor _
             ‚Ä¢ rinvunitor _).
  Defined.

  
B: bicat
x: B
mx, mx': disp_mnd B x
m‚ÇÅ:= x,, mx: mnd B

HŒ≥: is_invertible_2cell (mnd_mor_endo l)
mnd_mor_laws to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data

  
B: bicat
x: B
mx, mx': disp_mnd B x
m‚ÇÅ:= x,, mx: mnd B
m‚ÇÇ:= x,, mx': mnd B
Hl: mx -->[ id‚ÇÅ x] mx'
l:= id‚ÇÅ x,, Hl: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß

mnd_mor_laws to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data

    
B: bicat
x: B
mx, mx': disp_mnd B x
m‚ÇÅ:= x,, mx: mnd B
m‚ÇÇ:= x,, mx': mnd B

linvunitor
  (pr1 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data)
‚Ä¢ (unit_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ
   ‚ñπ pr1 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data) =
(rinvunitor
   (pr1 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data)
 ‚Ä¢ (pr1 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data
    ‚óÉ unit_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ))
‚Ä¢ pr2 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data
B: bicat
x: B
mx, mx': disp_mnd B x
m‚ÇÅ:= x,, mx: mnd B
m‚ÇÇ:= x,, mx': mnd B

l:= id‚ÇÅ x,, Hl: mnd B ‚ü¶ m‚ÇÅ, m‚ÇÇ ‚üß

((((lassociator
      (pr1 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data)
      (endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ) (endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ)
    ‚Ä¢ (pr2 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data
       ‚ñπ endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ))
   ‚Ä¢ rassociator (endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ)
       (pr1 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data)
       (endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ))
  ‚Ä¢ (endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ
     ‚óÉ pr2 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data))
 ‚Ä¢ lassociator (endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ) (endo_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ)
     (pr1 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data))
‚Ä¢ (mult_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ
   ‚ñπ pr1 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data) =
(pr1 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data
 ‚óÉ mult_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ)
‚Ä¢ pr2 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data

    
B: bicat
x: B
mx, mx': disp_mnd B x

linvunitor
  (pr1 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data)
‚Ä¢ (unit_of_mnd m‚ÇÇ
   ‚ñπ pr1 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data) =

   (pr1 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data)
 ‚Ä¢ (pr1 to_equivalence_mnd_help_right_adj_data
    ‚óÉ unit_of_mnd m‚ÇÅ))
